text: This is Justice Roberts - who @realdonaldtrump is publicly criticizing. en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_R… This President Trump - who is delivering the criticism. en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donald… I will let you all decide. Enjoy the holiday. Happy Thanksgiving.

You side with criminals (Saudi Arabia and elsewhere) over your own intelligence units, you strip the press of credentials, you separate families, you enrich yourself financially from your position, you prosecute your political enemies and you put troops on the border

as a political stunt. You are impulsive and have no guard rails. If someone disagrees with you on one single thing - no matter whether they are right or wrong or whether you understand the facts - you openly criticize. Other than that, sir, you are a good President.
You have dragged America further down in your rhetoric and actions - by politicizing the Judicial system. This is consistent with your Presidency from the "get go."

These are the words and actions of an authoritarian, a dictator. You possess no respect and understanding of the law. Moreover, you are wrong statistically. You possess a corrosive view towards the fundamental virtues of "checks and balances." You have a simplistic view of the

judiciary and the rules of law. Everything is about you - and you have consistently given into your impulses and ignored the facts. It takes alot to get a Chief Justic make his remarks - but you succeeded in doing so.
